# Generated extraction artifacts produced by the state `extract_*.py` adapters
# (committed as durable text-side fixtures, consumed by the loaders and the
# artifact-regression tests; never hand-edited — regenerate with the adapter).
#
# `linguist-generated`: mark as generated so GitHub collapses them in PRs and
# excludes them from language statistics.
#
# NOTE: line-count-based review limits (e.g. cubic's 50k-changed-line cap) are
# driven by GitHub's RAW diff line count, which `.gitattributes` does NOT
# reduce (`-diff` / `linguist-generated` only affect display + language stats).
# These artifacts are therefore serialized ONE SECTION PER LINE by the adapters
# (not indent=2 pretty-print) to keep their committed line count small — see
# the write step in extract_big_game.py.
ingestion/states/*/extracted/*.json linguist-generated
